00:34:17,422 --> 00:34:26,023
- I...am nothing like you.
- Sure you are. You just don't know it yet.

267
00:34:38,864 --> 00:34:41,424
- What do we got?
- Bar fight. Multiple knife wounds.

268
00:34:44,025 --> 00:34:46,026
What? Is this a joke?
The guy's fine.

269
00:34:46,105 --> 00:34:47,544
Where is he?

270
00:34:47,664 --> 00:34:48,224
I said where is he!

271
00:34:48,305 --> 00:34:49,145
I don't know who he is.

272
00:34:49,265 --> 00:34:51,706
I can help you.

273
