Six years I've been here. No one
knew me and then you show up!

274
00:35:01,147 --> 00:35:04,266
- And the next day, she's dead!
- I tried to warn you.

275
00:35:04,346 --> 00:35:07,187
- Why don't you tell me it was Victor?
- I didn't know!

276
00:35:10,667 --> 00:35:14,349
I swear on my son's life! I didn't...

277
00:35:20,929 --> 00:35:23,369
Victor's appetites were
becoming too public.

278
00:35:23,489 --> 00:35:26,690
I had to lock him up.
He thought I'd betrayed him.

279
00:35:26,890 --> 00:35:30,850
Went AWOL.
He said he was coming after all of us.

280
00:35:31,170 --> 00:35:34,409
You didn't come to warn me.
You came to save your own ass.

281
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:37,130
So what's your plan, captain?

282
00:35:37,210 --> 00:35:38,890
You can't beat him, Logan,
you know you can't.

283
00:35:39,170 --> 00:35:40,851
I'm gonna find him and kill him.

284
00:35:42,371 --> 00:35:44,611
I can give you the tools to defeat him.

285
00:35:48,772 --> 00:35:53,612
- So we can still save the others.
