286
00:35:54,612 --> 00:35:56,652
I promise you two things:

287
00:35:56,772 --> 00:35:59,733
You'll suffer more pain than
any other man can endure,

288
00:35:59,813 --> 00:36:02,213
but you'll have your revenge.

289
00:36:04,294 --> 00:36:08,093
If I come with you, I'm coming for blood.

290
00:36:09,133 --> 00:36:12,095
No law, no code of conduct.

291
00:36:12,455 --> 00:36:16,375
You point me in the right direction
and you get the hell out of my way.

292
00:36:54,579 --> 00:36:55,379
When it starts,

293
00:36:55,899 --> 00:36:58,940
whatever the reason is
that you're doing this,

294
00:36:59,060 --> 00:37:02,020
focus on that. Maybe it will help.

295
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:04,581
Trust me, I've been through worse.

296
00:37:04,661 --> 00:37:06,020
No you haven't.

297
00:37:07,261 --> 00:37:08,301
We are ready.

298
00:37:10,342 --> 00:37:15,181
We're gonna make you indestructible,
but first, we're gonna have to destroy you.

299
00:37:18,021 --> 00:37:21,423
Remember what we were
looking for in Africa?

300
00:37:21,503 --> 00:37:22,343
I remember.

301
00:37:22,423 --> 00:37:23,222
Well, I found it.

302
00:37:25,623 --> 00:37:29,342
It helped us create a...
metal compound so strong

303
00:37:29,422 --> 00:37:32,263
that you will be able to
withstand virtually anything.

304
00:37:32,383 --> 00:37:34,903
It's called Adamantium.

305
00:37:35,783 --> 00:37:38,785
I can't put Victor down myself, Logan.

306
00:37:39,465 --> 00:37:44,184
To kill him, you're gonna have to
embrace the other side,

307
00:37:45,625 --> 00:37:47,745
become the animal.

308
00:37:49,505 --> 00:37:51,026
Let's do this.

309
00:37:51,745 --> 00:37:53,065
