00:48:58,940 --> 00:48:59,739
Good morning.

400
00:49:03,019 --> 00:49:05,180
Oh, it fits you beautifully!

401
00:49:06,821 --> 00:49:07,940
I brought you some...

402
00:49:16,621 --> 00:49:19,222
<i>Weapon X is in the barn.
He just murdered two civilians.</i>

403
00:49:19,302 --> 00:49:22,422
Blow him to bits.
Let's see if he can survive that.

404
00:49:34,463 --> 00:49:36,024
<i>Fire at will.</i>

405
00:49:44,745 --> 00:49:45,945
Come and get me!

406
00:49:58,667 --> 00:50:00,026
Blow his head up.

407
00:50:00,426 --> 00:50:01,627
Damn!

408
00:50:36,350 --> 00:50:38,190
Alpha One, do not lose him!

409
00:50:46,151 --> 00:50:48,272
<i>Alfa 2, target's coming to you!</i>

410
00:51:37,658 --> 00:51:39,417
Pull up! Pull up!

411
00:52:44,325 --> 00:52:46,165
<i>Zero, is Logan dead?</i>

412
00:52:46,165 --> 00:52:47,724
Don't know, I'm down.

413
00:52:57,667 --> 00:52:59,386
<i>Zero, come in!</i>

414
00:53:03,447 --> 00:53:05,166
<i>You tried to kill me.</i>

415
00:53:05,606 --> 00:53:06,607
Logan?

416
00:53:06,727 --> 00:53:07,847
Where is Victor?

417
00:53:07,927 --> 00:53:09,688
Come back to base.

418
00:53:09,808 --> 00:53:11,727
I'll explain everything,
we'll take Victor down together.

419
00:53:11,807 --> 00:53:13,288
