420
00:53:13,368 --> 00:53:15,929
After I've killed Victor,
I'm coming for you.

421
00:53:18,568 --> 00:53:20,488
<i>Logan, listen to me.</i>

422
00:53:20,569 --> 00:53:22,968
If you go down this road, you're
not gonna like what you find.

423
00:53:24,089 --> 00:53:28,129
You wanted the animal, Colonel?
You got it.

424
00:53:32,371 --> 00:53:34,929
Those were good people back there.

425
00:53:35,170 --> 00:53:37,170
Innocent people.

426
00:53:42,771 --> 00:53:46,491
It's funny how good innocent people
tend to die around you.

427
00:54:09,774 --> 00:54:12,134
Zero never stood a chance.

428
00:54:12,214 --> 00:54:15,815
The only thing that'll take him down
is an Adamantium bullet

429
00:54:23,055 --> 00:54:25,695
This facility is compromised.
Prep transport.

430
00:54:34,497 --> 00:54:36,178
Colonel, this is turning into a disaster.

431
00:54:36,658 --> 00:54:38,777
- Don't worry, we'll stop him.
- Really?

432
00:54:38,897 --> 00:54:41,978
You've just spent half a billion
dollars making him indestructible.

433
00:54:45,058 --> 00:54:46,378
- Sir?
- Yes.

434
00:54:46,498 --> 00:54:49,418
The young mutant you've been looking for?
We found him.

435
00:54:49,898 --> 00:54:52,419
General, Logan isn't the only
piece in this puzzle.

436
00:54:52,499 --> 00:54:56,299
