00:56:02,547 --> 00:56:05,226
- Rounding who up?
- Leave it alone.

459
00:56:05,307 --> 00:56:07,187
Rounding who up, John?

460
00:56:07,747 --> 00:56:09,667
Hey! God damn it, John!

461
00:56:09,747 --> 00:56:11,988
