465
00:56:18,428 --> 00:56:20,909
Stryker'd say we would
make a difference.

466
00:56:21,228 --> 00:56:23,829
Protecting people from the bad ones.

467
00:56:24,390 --> 00:56:26,789
How are you gonna take
Victor down, Logan?

468
00:56:27,390 --> 00:56:30,751
- Remember that stuff in Africa?
